## Migration tracking tables

For reference when writing migrations that interact with tracking:

| Table | Tracks | Used by |
|-------|--------|---------|
| `schema_migrations` | Pre-migration versions | golang-migrate |
| `schema_migrations_post` | Post-migration versions | golang-migrate |
| `schema_checksums` | GORM struct checksums | Custom migrator |

